PN,38501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FThe Royal Navy said it has carried out
OL,7,Fa three-month long "unbroken watch" on
OL,8,FRussian warships and accompanying
OL,9,Fvessels in UK waters including a
OL,10,Ffrigate which fired a warning shot on
OL,11,Fa British yacht.
OL,13,FFive navy ships have been involved in
OL,14,Fthe monitoring of the Admiral
OL,15,FGrigorovich, which opened fire in the
OL,16,Fincident involving the yacht Bright
OL,17,FFuture south of the Isle of Wight on
OL,18,FJune 16.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@cO]
