OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FA Royal Navy spokesman said that the
OL,7,FAdmiral Grigorovich was present in the
OL,8,FChannel from April 30 to May 4, May 8
OL,9,Fto 12, and May 22 to 28.
OL,11,FHe said: "Royal Navy warships and
OL,12,Fhelicopters have maintained an
OL,13,Funbroken watch on Russian frigates and
OL,14,Ftheir accompanying vessels in UK
OL,15,Fwaters for nearly three months ` and
OL,16,Fthat vigil continues today.
OL,26,@sD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,F"Patrol ships HMS Tyne, Ledbury,
OL,7,FSevern, Mersey and Type 23 frigate HMS
OL,8,FSutherland tracked the Russian navy's
OL,9,FAdmiral Grigorovich throughout May and
OL,10,Finto June.
OL,12,F"This followed a concerted effort in
OL,13,FApril, when Royal Navy ships or
OL,14,Faircraft monitored the Russian warship
OL,15,Fevery single day."
OL,17,FThe yacht incident came two days after
OL,18,FRussian shadow fleet tanker MV Smyrtos
OL,19,Fwas seized on June 14.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FThe Navy spokesman said: "Green berets
OL,7,Ffrom 42 Commando, alongside specially-
OL,8,Ftrained law enforcement officers from
OL,9,Fthe National Crime Agency, boarded the
OL,10,Fvessel Smyrtos in a six-hour mission
OL,11,Fsupported by HMS Sutherland, HMS
OL,12,FLedbury, Merlin Mk4s from the Commando
OL,13,FHelicopter Force, Wildcat helicopters,
OL,14,Fand RAF Chinooks and P8 Poseidon
OL,15,Faircraft."
OL,17,FMinister for the armed forces Louise
OL,18,FSandher-Jones said: "The Royal Navy is
OL,19,Fon watch every hour of every day,
OL,20,Fprotecting our waters and helping to
OL,21,Fkeep the UK secure.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUwD@JO]zD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,F"As Russian naval activity around the
OL,7,FUK continues, our sailors and aircrew
OL,8,Fhave worked alongside Nato allies and
OL,9,FIreland to track, monitor and deter
OL,10,Fvessels operating near our shores.
OL,12,F"I pay tribute to the men and women
OL,13,Fwho carry out this vital work every
OL,14,Fday. Their professionalism sends a
OL,15,Fclear message: we are always on watch,
OL,16,Fand we will always defend our nation,
OL,17,Four waters and our critical
OL,18,Finfrastructure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FRoyal Navy Fleet Commander, Vice
OL,7,FAdmiral Steve Moorhouse, said: "In
OL,8,Frecent months, the Royal Navy has
OL,9,Fworked tirelessly to safeguard UK
OL,10,Fwaters in response to increased
OL,11,FRussian naval activity.
OL,13,F"Our sailors, ships and aircraft have
OL,14,Fmaintained a constant watch, helping
OL,15,Fto protect the UK's security and
OL,16,Freassure our allies.
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,F"Their professionalism, dedication and
OL,7,Fteamwork demonstrate the Royal Navy's
OL,8,Fability to respond quickly to emerging
OL,9,Fchallenges with Nato partners to keep
OL,10,Four seas safe and secure."
OL,12,FThe Navy spokesman said the monitoring
OL,13,Foperation also included HMS Tyne
OL,14,Fobserving the Grigorovich "conduct a
OL,15,Fraft-up with Russian Amur-class supply
OL,16,Fship PM-82 near the Galloper Wind Farm
OL,17,Foff the coast of Suffolk".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZO]vD@[OUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FHe said: "The supply ship operates as
OL,7,Fa floating workshop capable of
OL,8,Ftransferring fuel and stores to
OL,9,FRussian warships."
OL,11,FHe added that Type 23 frigate HMS
OL,12,FSomerset intercepted the Yury Ivanov,
OL,13,Fa Russian navy intelligence-gathering
OL,14,Fship.
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782490721
OL,3,CNavy carries out three-month 'unbroken
OL,4,Cwatch' of Russian warships in UK waters
OL,6,FThe spokesman said: "The operation was
OL,7,Fconducted alongside other Nato
OL,8,Fwarships and supported by maritime
OL,9,Fpatrol aircraft and vessels from the
OL,10,FIrish Defence Forces, ensuring
OL,11,Fcontinuous monitoring of the vessel's
OL,12,Fmovements."
OL,14,FHe added: "Somerset was subsequently
OL,15,Ftasked to sail from the Isles of
OL,16,FScilly to shadow the Ropucha-class
OL,17,FLanding Ship Transport Aleksander
OL,18,FShabalin and the tanker MV Mikhail
OL,19,FBritnev through the English Channel `
OL,20,Fthe latest chapter in a sustained
OL,21,Fmaritime surveillance mission."
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@KO]vD@KOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
